<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idc9bf6e44-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598" identifier="/us/usc/t43/s316a"><num value="316a">§ 316a.</num><heading> Definitions</heading>
<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">As used in this subchapter—</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0" id="idc9bf6e45-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598" identifier="/us/usc/t43/s316a/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> The term “person” means individual, partnership, corporation, or association.</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0" id="idc9bf6e46-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598" identifier="/us/usc/t43/s316a/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> The term “district” means any grazing district established under the provisions of <ref href="/us/usc/t43/s316b">section 316b of this title</ref>.</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0" id="idc9bf6e47-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598" identifier="/us/usc/t43/s316a/3"><num value="3">(3)</num><content> The term “Secretary” means the Secretary of the Interior.</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0" id="idc9bf6e48-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598" identifier="/us/usc/t43/s316a/4"><num value="4">(4)</num><content> The term “lessee” means the holder of any lease.</content>
</paragraph>
<sourceCredit id="idc9bf6e49-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598">(<ref href="/us/act/1927-03-04/ch513/s2">Mar. 4, 1927, ch. 513, § 2</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/44/1452">44 Stat. 1452</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idc9bf6e4a-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="idc9bf6e4b-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I76" topic="codification" id="idc9bf6e4c-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Codification</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section was formerly classified to <ref href="/us/usc/t48/s471a">section 471a of Title 48</ref>, Territories and Insular Possessions.</p>
</note>
</notes>
